node.text:
#Repost @britishvogue with @make_repost
・・・
Struggling to source some inspiration for your summer looks after a year of loungewear? #IrinaShayk has got you covered. In a homemade video, the super shares her go-to styling tips for summer 2021. Watch as she creates six different looks with her favourite pieces from her capsule collection for @TamaraMellon @amelietrem

node.text: Class is in session for @BritishVogue’s March 2020 issue @edward_enninful ❣️ Life lessons served at the link in bio 🎥😘 Directed by @BarbarAnastacio, styled by @DenaGia, produced by @TheRealMinnieCarver ✨

Get ready with me, as I pick the perfect outfit to meet @JPGaultierOfficial, for dinner in Paris! Out to celebrate the launch of his new, iconic fragrance ‘Scandal’.. 🖤
Special thanks @VogueParis and @TheLionsNY

node.title: Pre-Dinner prep in Paris w/ @JPGaultierOfficial and @VogueParis!
